refund for payment of conference ticket - if you buy a ticket for a conference paying with your own funds and you want to ask for a reimbursement
If you are a VAT payer - you add a line with a description: additional cost. On that line you add a net value. Then you add VAT to the total value on aa invoice. 
note that: you can settle an invoice within your own company and ask for a VAT return. 
If you are not a VAT payer - you add a line with a description: additional cost. On that line you add a gross value.
NOTE: if the conference is related to ucreate's product and work related to it - company can pay for the conference ticket. 
